data.description: This breathtaking and custom-built home is a must-see! Located on a gorgeous and peaceful 68.96 acre lot, featuring three finished and upgraded levels, perfect for multi-generational living or private guest lodging! With multiple kitchens, living areas, and plenty of room for everyone to enjoy, this home has granite countertops, a spacious kitchen island, an abundance of cabinet space, and a large family room with cathedral ceilings and wood beams. Also included are custom tile showers, a large whirlpool tub, walk-in cedar closet, and craft room on the terrace level! Beautiful views from the spacious screened-in porch, overlooking two private ponds, a pasture, and beautiful hardwoods leading to a private camping area and creek. An in-ground swimming pool surrounded by multi-level decks makes the perfect area for entertaining or a tranquil retreat. Five garages and 12x56 workshop. Brand new roof installed. Convenient access to I-20.
